node_6.subject: Klaus Mueller
node_6.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, go to the library at Oak Hill College at 8:00 am, work on his research paper on gentrification until 12:00 pm, have lunch at Hobbs Cafe at 12:30 pm, continue working on his research paper until 4:00 pm, take a break and go for a walk around the campus at 4:30 pm, return to the library and work on his research paper until 7:00 pm, have dinner at 7:30 pm.
